branchCategory.name: MY1
branchCategory.description: <p>Rodless Cylinder, mechanically jointed series 90-MY1 and 91-MY1 is great for long strokes with compact size and an integrated guide, the MY1 series rodless actuator provides an ideal solution.&nbsp;90-MY1 is made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing. 91-MY1 includes a "Lub-retainer" and is compatible with low dew point (40&deg;C) applications.&nbsp;Standard strokes are available up to 2000mm.</p>
